title: Open Wednesday, Aug 3rd from 4-7pm! 4 bed/2 bath Remodeled! AC!
posting_body: ['I have another home available at 2182 Marsh Ave, Pittsburg', 'OPEN HOUSE TIMES: Wednesday, August 3rd from 4-7pm for 201 Thomas Way', '*1223 Sq Feet', '*4 bedrooms (possible 4 bedrooms - additional room off the kitchen can be used as a bedroom, dining area or office )', '*2 bathrooms  - including New expanded Primary Bathroom (Large Shower, Vanity, toilet, luxury vinyl, Kohler Toilet)', '*Gorgeous kitchen with sleek granite, dishwasher, gas range, refrigerator and new microwave', '*Spacious Living room with new Solartube and LED recessed lighting', '*Dual pane windows', '*Ceiling fans in every bedroom', '*Forced air and Central AC - always maintained', '*Laminate and tile flooring throughout', '*Attached 2 car garage with interior and side yard access and gas/electric laundry hookups', 'Front and back landscaped with automatic sprinklers.', 'Gorgeous Backyard with lawn, trellis, patio!', 'Inviting Serene backyard with lawn area, fruit trees and handsome trellis really make this home stand out!', 'Warm, welcoming, well maintained 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with new upgrades!', 'Large living room with natural light from Solartube and LED recessed lighting.', 'Beautiful Kitchen with newly installed Solartube, sleek granite counters and gorgeous cabinetry.', 'Beautiful appliance package including new Microwave, Gas Burner range, dishwasher and top/bottom refrigerator.', 'New designer expanded primary bathroom with new shower, enclosure and doors, vanity, water efficient Kohler toilet and luxury vinyl flooring!', 'Well maintained furnace and AC unit and all bedrooms with ceiling fans.', 'Laminate and tile flooring throughout.', '2 car garage includes side by side laundry gas or electric hookups and interior side yard access.', 'Gorgeous fully landscaped backyard with lawn area w/automatic sprinklers, Trellis and large concrete patio.', 'Very close..within minutes to freeway and Bart access and shopping.', 'Rancho Mendanos Elementary, Starbucks, Grocery, restaurants and banking close by!', 'Tenant responsible for all utilities and maintenance of yard.', 'Non-Smoking Home - no exceptions even if you smoke outside.', 'Owner is licensed Realtor in the state of California.', '$2,695 per month / Does not include utilities.']
